headline: AvalonBay: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: ARLINGTON, Va. (AP) — AvalonBay Communities Inc. (AVB) on Wednesday reported a key measure of profitability in its third quarter.  The results missed Wall Street expectations.  The real estate investment trust, based in Arlington, Virginia, said it had funds from operations of $394.2 million, or $2.75 per share, in the period.
